<HEAD>With PM-Trade Bjt</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By The Associated Press</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
 Here, at a glance, are highlights of the federal trade bill passed by the <ORGANIZATION> Senate </ORGANIZATION> and which faces a likely presidential veto:
