...'' to UPDATE with Aspin prediction of passage; Picks up 6th graf
pvs, bgng: ``The Pentagon ...''</NOTE>
<BYLINE>By TIM AHERN</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
